<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AquaSis - Área do Cliente e Resultados</title>
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles-consulta.css">

</head>
<body>

    <nav class="top-navbar">
        <div class="brand-header">
            <div class="logo-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="brand-name">AquaSis</span>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="main-container">
        
        <span class="breadcrumb">Área do Cliente</span>
        <h1 class="greeting">Olá, Fazenda Vale Verde</h1>

        <h2 class="section-title">Ações Rápidas</h2>
        <div class="actions-grid">
            
            <a href="#" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="action-text">Agendar<br>nova coleta</div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="action-text">Solicitar<br>análise</div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="action-text">Histórico<br>de coletas</div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="action-text">Histórico<br>de laudos</div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="action-text">Meus<br>laudos</div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="8" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"></line><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"></line><line x1="8" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"></line><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="3.01" y2="6"></line><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="3.01" y2="12"></line><line x1="3" y1="18" x2="3.01" y2="18"></line></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="action-text">Faturas<br>pendentes</div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="8.5" cy="7" r="4"></circle><line x1="20" y1="8" x2="20" y2="14"></line><line x1="23" y1="11" x2="17" y2="11"></line></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="action-text">Adicionar<br>usuários</div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-icon" style="color: #6b7280;">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="action-text">Ver mais</div>
            </a>

        </div>

        <div class="promo-banner">
            <h3>Atualize seus dados de faturamento</h3>
            <p>Adicione ou revise seus dados cadastrais para facilitar a emissão de notas fiscais e boletos.</p>
            <button class="btn-banner">ATUALIZAR DADOS</button>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-title">Laudos Técnicos Mais Recentes</h2>
        
        <div class="results-container">
            
            <div class="result-item">
                <div class="status-icon pending">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="result-info">
                    <div class="result-type">Análise Bacteriológica</div>
                    <div class="result-date">30 de out <span>|</span> 2023</div>
                    <div class="result-location">Poço Artesiano Sede</div>
                </div>
                <button class="btn-download-pdf disabled" disabled>
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"></line><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"></line></svg>
                    Em Análise
                </button>
            </div>

            <div class="result-item">
                <div class="status-icon ready">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="result-info">
                    <div class="result-type">Físico-Química de Efluentes</div>
                    <div class="result-date">16 de out <span>|</span> 2023</div>
                    <div class="result-location">Caixa Separadora - Setor Sul</div>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="btn-download-pdf">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line></svg>
                    Baixar PDF
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="result-item">
                <div class="status-icon ready">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="result-info">
                    <div class="result-type">Análise de Água Potável MS</div>
                    <div class="result-date">29 de out <span>|</span> 2022</div>
                    <div class="result-location">Reservatório Principal</div>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="btn-download-pdf">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line></svg>
                    Baixar PDF
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="results-footer">
                <button class="btn-view-all">VEJA TODOS OS LAUDOS</button>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>